"As noted before, Rupert‚Äôs condition and Lemma 18 imply in particular that
max_{P} ‚ü™ R(Œ±) M(Œ∏‚ÇÅ, œÜ‚ÇÅ), P, w ‚ü´ < max_{P} ‚ü™ M(Œ∏‚ÇÇ, œÜ‚ÇÇ), P, w ‚ü´"
